            ],
            "angle": 0,
            "content": "一、填空题"
        },
        {
            "type": "text",
            "bbox": [
                0.055,
                0.155,
                0.336,
                0.17
            ],
            "angle": 0,
            "content": "(1)【答案】 \\(x - 3y - z + 4 = 0.\\)"
        },
        {
            "type": "text",
            "bbox": [
                0.086,
                0.176,
                0.497,
                0.191
            ],
            "angle": 0,
            "content": "【解】 显然所求平面的法向量为 \\(n = \\{-1,3,1\\}\\)"
        },
        {
            "type": "text",
            "bbox": [
                0.087,
                0.197,
                0.692,
                0.213
            ],
            "angle": 0,
            "content": "所求平面为 \\(-(x - 1) + 3(y - 2) + (z + 1) = 0\\) ，即 \\(x - 3y - z + 4 = 0\\)"
        },
        {
            "type": "text",
            "bbox": [
                0.057,
                0.218,
                0.195,
                0.234
            ],
            "angle": 0,
            "content": "(2)【答案】 \\(\\mathrm{e}^{2a}\\)."
        },
        {
            "type": "text",
            "bbox": [
                0.087,
                0.241,
                0.569,
                0.276
            ],
            "angle": 0,
            "content": "【解】 \\(\\lim_{x\\to \\infty}\\left(\\frac{x + a}{x - a}\\right)^x = \\lim_{x\\to \\infty}\\left[\\left(1 + \\frac{2a}{x - a}\\right)^{\\frac{x - a}{2a}}\\right]^x\\cdot \\frac{2a}{x - a} = \\mathrm{e}^{2a}.\\)"
        },
        {
            "type": "text",
            "bbox": [
                0.057,
                0.282,
                0.182,
                0.298
            ],
            "angle": 0,
            "content": "（3）【答案】1."
        },
        {
            "type": "text",
            "bbox": [
                0.087,
                0.303,
                0.401,
                0.34
            ],
            "angle": 0,
            "content": "【解】 \\(f[f(x)] = \\left\\{ \\begin{array}{ll}1, & |f(x)|\\leqslant 1,\\\\ 0, & |f(x)| > 1. \\end{array} \\right.\\)"
        },
        {
            "type": "text",
            "bbox": [
                0.088,
                0.345,
                0.411,
                0.362
            ],
            "angle": 0,
            "content": "因为 \\(|f(x)| \\leqslant 1\\) ，所以 \\(f[f(x)] = 1\\)"
        },
        {
            "type": "text",
            "bbox": [
                0.057,
                0.369,
                0.281,
                0.397
            ],
            "angle": 0,
            "content": "(4)【答案】 \\(\\frac{1}{2}\\left(1 - \\frac{1}{\\mathrm{e}^4}\\right)\\)."
        },
        {
            "type": "text",
            "bbox": [
                0.087,
                0.405,
                0.286,
                0.421
            ],
            "angle": 0,
            "content": "【解】 改变积分次序得"
        },
        {
            "type": "equation",
            "bbox": [
                0.196,
                0.426,
                0.821,
                0.457
            ],
            "angle": 0,
            "content": "\\[\n\\int_ {0} ^ {2} \\mathrm {d} x \\int_ {x} ^ {2} \\mathrm {e} ^ {- y ^ {2}} \\mathrm {d} y = \\int_ {0} ^ {2} \\mathrm {e} ^ {- y ^ {2}} \\mathrm {d} y \\int_ {0} ^ {y} \\mathrm {d} x = \\int_ {0} ^ {2} y \\mathrm {e} ^ {- y ^ {2}} \\mathrm {d} y = - \\frac {1}{2} \\mathrm {e} ^ {- y ^ {2}} \\left| _ {0} ^ {2} = \\frac {1}{2} \\left(1 - \\frac {1}{\\mathrm {e} ^ {4}}\\right). \\right.\n\\]"
        },
        {
            "type": "text",
            "bbox": [
                0.057,
                0.465,
                0.185,
                0.481
            ],
            "angle": 0,
            "content": "（5）【答案】2."
        },
        {
            "type": "text",
            "bbox": [
                0.087,
                0.485,
                0.827,
                0.564
            ],
            "angle": 0,
            "content": "【解】 \\(\\mathbf{A} = (\\pmb{\\alpha}_{1}^{\\mathrm{T}},\\pmb{\\alpha}_{2}^{\\mathrm{T}},\\pmb{\\alpha}_{3}^{\\mathrm{T}},\\pmb{\\alpha}_{4}^{\\mathrm{T}}) = \\begin{bmatrix} 1 & 2 & 3 & 4\\\\ 2 & 3 & 4 & 5\\\\ 3 & 4 & 5 & 6\\\\ 4 & 5 & 6 & 7 \\end{bmatrix} \\rightarrow \\begin{bmatrix} 1 & 2 & 3 & 4\\\\ 0 & -1 & -2 & -3\\\\ 0 & -2 & -4 & -6\\\\ 0 & -3 & -6 & -9 \\end{bmatrix} \\rightarrow \\begin{bmatrix} 1 & 2 & 3 & 4\\\\ 0 & 1 & 2 & 3\\\\ 0 & 0 & 0 & 0\\\\ 0 & 0 & 0 & 0 \\end{bmatrix},\\)"
        },
        {
            "type": "text",
            "bbox": [
                0.089,
                0.571,
                0.414,
                0.586
            ],
            "angle": 0,
            "content": "因为 \\(r(\\mathbf{A}) = 2\\) ，所以该向量组的秩为2."
        },
        {
            "type": "title",
            "bbox": [
                0.057,
                0.593,
                0.146,
                0.608
            ],
            "angle": 0,
            "content": "二、选择题"
        },
        {
            "type": "text",
            "bbox": [
                0.057,
                0.614,
                0.206,
                0.629
            ],
            "angle": 0,
            "content": "(1)【答案】 (A)."
        },
        {
            "type": "text",
            "bbox": [
                0.087,
                0.634,
                0.69,
                0.651
            ],
            "angle": 0,
            "content": "【解】 \\(F^{\\prime}(x) = f(\\mathrm{e}^{-x})(\\mathrm{e}^{-x})^{\\prime} - f(x) = -\\mathrm{e}^{-x}f(\\mathrm{e}^{-x}) - f(x)\\)，应选(A)."
        },
        {
            "type": "text",
            "bbox": [
                0.057,
                0.657,
                0.206,
                0.671
            ],
            "angle": 0,
            "content": "(2)【答案】 (A)."
        },
        {
            "type": "text",
            "bbox": [
                0.087,
                0.677,
                0.344,
                0.693
            ],
            "angle": 0,
            "content": "【解】 由 \\( f^{\\prime}(x) = [f(x)]^{2} \\) 得"
        },
        {
            "type": "equation",
            "bbox": [
                0.168,
                0.698,
                0.556,
                0.736
            ],
            "angle": 0,
            "content": "\\[\n\\begin{array}{l} f ^ {\\prime \\prime} (x) = 2 f (x) f ^ {\\prime} (x) = 2 [ f (x) ] ^ {3}, \\\\ f ^ {\\prime \\prime} (x) = 2 \\times 3 [ f (x) ] ^ {2} f ^ {\\prime} (x) = 3! [ f (x) ] ^ {4}, \\\\ \\end{array}\n\\]"
        },
        {
            "type": "text",
            "bbox": [
                0.09,
                0.741,
                0.486,
                0.757
            ],
            "angle": 0,
            "content": "由归纳法得 \\(f^{(n)}(x) = n!\\left[f(x)\\right]^{n + 1}\\)，应选(A)."
        },
        {
            "type": "text",
            "bbox": [
                0.057,
                0.763,
                0.205,
                0.778
            ],
            "angle": 0,
            "content": "（3）【答案】 (C)."
        },
        {
            "type": "text",
            "bbox": [
                0.087,
                0.783,
                0.657,
                0.817
            ],
            "angle": 0,
            "content": "【解】因为 \\(\\left|\\frac{\\sin n\\alpha}{n^2}\\right| \\leqslant \\frac{1}{n^2}\\) 且 \\(\\sum_{n=1}^{\\infty} \\frac{1}{n^2}\\) 收敛，所以 \\(\\sum_{n=1}^{\\infty} \\frac{\\sin n\\alpha}{n^2}\\) 绝对收敛；"
        },
        {
            "type": "text",
            "bbox": [
                0.088,
                0.824,
                0.554,
                0.857
            ],
            "angle": 0,
            "content": "因为 \\(\\sum_{n = 1}^{\\infty}\\frac{1}{\\sqrt{n}}\\) 发散，所以 \\(\\sum_{n = 1}^{\\infty}\\left(\\frac{\\sin n\\alpha}{n^2} -\\frac{1}{\\sqrt{n}}\\right)\\) 发散，应选(C)."
        },
        {
            "type": "text",
            "bbox": [
                0.057,
                0.865,
                0.205,
                0.879
            ],
            "angle": 0,
            "content": "（4）【答案】 (D)."
        },
        {
            "type": "text",
            "bbox": [
                0.087,
                0.886,
                0.896,
                0.914
            ],
            "angle": 0,
            "content": "【解】因为 \\(\\lim_{x\\to 0}\\frac{f(x)}{1 - \\cos{x}} = 2\\) ，所以由极限保号性，存在 \\(\\delta >0\\) ，当 \\(0 < |x| < \\delta\\) 时， \\(\\frac{f(x)}{1 - \\cos{x}} >0.\\)"
        },
        {
            "type": "text",
            "bbox": [
                0.088,
                0.921,
                0.72,
                0.937
            ],
            "angle": 0,
            "content": "因为 \\(1 - \\cos x > 0\\) ，所以 \\(f(x) > 0 = f(0)\\) ，故 \\(x = 0\\) 为极小值点，应选(D)."
        }
    ],
    [
        {
            "type": "text",
