            ],
            "angle": 0,
            "content": "【解】令 \\(k_{1}\\pmb{\\alpha}_{1} + k_{2}(\\pmb{\\alpha}_{1} - \\pmb{\\alpha}_{2}) = \\mathbf{0}\\) ，即 \\((k_{1} + k_{2})\\pmb{\\alpha}_{1} - k_{2}\\pmb{\\alpha}_{2} = \\mathbf{0}\\)"
        },
        {
            "type": "text",
            "bbox": [
                0.093,
                0.112,
                0.881,
                0.126
            ],
            "angle": 0,
            "content": "因为 \\(\\alpha_{1},\\alpha_{2}\\) 线性无关，所以 \\(k_{1} + k_{2} = 0, - k_{2} = 0\\) ，或 \\(k_{1} = 0,k_{2} = 0\\) ，即 \\(\\alpha_{1},\\alpha_{1} - \\alpha_{2}\\) 线性无关，"
        },
        {
            "type": "text",
            "bbox": [
                0.093,
                0.133,
                0.938,
                0.167
            ],
            "angle": 0,
            "content": "又因为 \\(\\alpha_{1},\\alpha_{1} - \\alpha_{2}\\) 为齐次线性方程组 \\(AX = 0\\) 的解，所以 \\(\\alpha_{1},\\alpha_{1} - \\alpha_{2}\\) 为齐次线性方程组 \\(AX = 0\\) 的基础解系；"
        },
        {
            "type": "text",
            "bbox": [
                0.062,
                0.177,
                0.935,
                0.228
            ],
            "angle": 0,
            "content": "而 \\(\\frac{\\pmb{\\beta}_1 + \\pmb{\\beta}_2}{2}\\) 为非齐次线性方程组 \\(AX = b\\) 的解，故 \\(k_{1}\\alpha_{1} + k_{2}(\\alpha_{1} - \\alpha_{2}) + \\frac{\\pmb{\\beta}_{1} + \\pmb{\\beta}_{2}}{2}\\) 为 \\(AX = b\\) 的通解，应选(B).三、"
        },
        {
            "type": "text",
            "bbox": [
                0.065,
                0.236,
                0.476,
                0.264
            ],
            "angle": 0,
            "content": "(1)【解】 \\(\\int_0^1\\frac{\\ln(1 + x)}{(2 - x)^2}\\mathrm{d}x = \\int_0^1\\ln (1 + x)\\mathrm{d}\\left(\\frac{1}{2 - x}\\right)\\)"
        },
        {
            "type": "equation",
            "bbox": [
                0.065,
                0.236,
                0.697,
                0.34
            ],
            "angle": 0,
            "content": "\\[\n\\begin{array}{l} = \\left. \\frac {\\ln (1 + x)}{2 - x} \\right| _ {0} ^ {1} + \\int_ {0} ^ {1} \\frac {1}{(x - 2) (x + 1)} d x \\\\ = \\ln 2 + \\frac {1}{3} \\ln \\left| \\frac {x - 2}{x + 1} \\right| _ {0} ^ {1} = \\ln 2 - \\frac {2}{3} \\ln 2 = \\frac {1}{3} \\ln 2. \\\\ \\end{array}\n\\]"
        },
        {
            "type": "text",
            "bbox": [
                0.064,
                0.349,
                0.372,
                0.376
            ],
            "angle": 0,
            "content": "(2)【解】 \\(\\frac{\\partial z}{\\partial x} = 2f_1' + y\\cos x \\cdot f_2'\\),"
        },
        {
            "type": "equation",
            "bbox": [
                0.098,
                0.385,
                0.721,
                0.436
            ],
            "angle": 0,
            "content": "\\[\n\\begin{array}{l} \\frac {\\partial^ {2} z}{\\partial x \\partial y} = 2 \\left(- f _ {1 1} ^ {\\prime \\prime} + \\sin x \\cdot f _ {1 2} ^ {\\prime \\prime}\\right) + \\cos x \\cdot f _ {2} ^ {\\prime} + y \\cos x \\left(- f _ {2 1} ^ {\\prime \\prime} + \\sin x \\cdot f _ {2 2} ^ {\\prime \\prime}\\right) \\\\ = - 2 f _ {1 1} ^ {\\prime \\prime} + (2 \\sin x - y \\cos x) \\cdot f _ {1 2} ^ {\\prime \\prime} + \\cos x \\cdot f _ {2} ^ {\\prime} + y \\sin x \\cos x \\cdot f _ {2 2} ^ {\\prime \\prime}. \\\\ \\end{array}\n\\]"
        },
        {
            "type": "text",
            "bbox": [
                0.064,
                0.444,
                0.609,
                0.459
            ],
            "angle": 0,
            "content": "（3）【解】 特征方程为 \\(\\lambda^2 + 4\\lambda + 4 = 0\\)，特征根为 \\(\\lambda_1 = \\lambda_2 = -2\\)"
        },
        {
            "type": "text",
            "bbox": [
                0.093,
                0.466,
                0.515,
                0.481
            ],
            "angle": 0,
            "content": "\\(y^{\\prime \\prime} + 4y^{\\prime} + 4y = 0\\) 的通解为 \\(y = (C_1 + C_2x)\\mathrm{e}^{-2x}\\)"
        },
        {
            "type": "text",
            "bbox": [
                0.093,
                0.49,
                0.662,
                0.515
            ],
            "angle": 0,
            "content": "令 \\(y^{\\prime \\prime} + 4y^{\\prime} + 4y = \\mathrm{e}^{-2x}\\) 的特解为 \\(y_0(x) = ax^2\\mathrm{e}^{-2x}\\) ，代入得 \\(a = \\frac{1}{2}\\)"
        },
        {
            "type": "text",
            "bbox": [
                0.094,
                0.524,
                0.376,
                0.539
            ],
            "angle": 0,
            "content": "故 \\(y^{\\prime \\prime} + 4y^{\\prime} + 4y = \\mathrm{e}^{-2x}\\) 的通解为"
        },
        {
            "type": "equation",
            "bbox": [
                0.29,
                0.548,
                0.74,
                0.575
            ],
            "angle": 0,
            "content": "\\[\ny = (C _ {1} + C _ {2} x) \\mathrm {e} ^ {- 2 x} + \\frac {1}{2} x ^ {2} \\mathrm {e} ^ {- 2 x} (C _ {1}, C _ {2} \\text {为 任 意 常 数}).\n\\]"
        },
        {
            "type": "text",
            "bbox": [
                0.064,
                0.583,
                0.535,
                0.615
            ],
            "angle": 0,
            "content": "四、【解】 由 \\(\\lim_{n\\to \\infty}\\left|\\frac{a_{n + 1}}{a_n}\\right| = 1\\) 得幂级数的收敛半径 \\(R = 1\\)"
        },
        {
            "type": "text",
            "bbox": [
                0.091,
                0.622,
                0.708,
                0.636
            ],
            "angle": 0,
            "content": "当 \\(x = \\pm 1\\) 时，\\((2n + 1)(\\pm 1)^n \\to \\infty (n \\to \\infty)\\)，即 \\(x = \\pm 1\\) 时，幂级数发散，"
        },
        {
            "type": "text",
            "bbox": [
                0.091,
                0.644,
                0.335,
                0.657
            ],
            "angle": 0,
            "content": "故幂级数的收敛域为 \\((-1, 1)\\)."
        },
        {
            "type": "text",
            "bbox": [
                0.091,
                0.667,
                0.324,
                0.697
            ],
            "angle": 0,
            "content": "令 \\(S(x) = \\sum_{n=0}^{\\infty}(2n+1)x^{n}\\),"
        },
        {
            "type": "text",
            "bbox": [
                0.091,
                0.703,
                0.56,
                0.734
            ],
            "angle": 0,
            "content": "则 \\(S(x) = 2x\\sum_{n = 1}^{\\infty}nx^{n - 1} + \\sum_{n = 0}^{\\infty}x^{n} = 2x(\\sum_{n = 1}^{\\infty}x^{n})^{\\prime} + \\frac{1}{1 - x}\\)"
        },
        {
            "type": "equation",
            "bbox": [
                0.169,
                0.743,
                0.472,
                0.769
            ],
            "angle": 0,
            "content": "\\[\n= 2 x \\left(\\frac {x}{1 - x}\\right) ^ {\\prime} + \\frac {1}{1 - x} = \\frac {1 + x}{(1 - x) ^ {2}}.\n\\]"
        },
        {
            "type": "title",
            "bbox": [
                0.064,
                0.778,
                0.212,
                0.792
            ],
            "angle": 0,
            "content": "五、【解】 方法一"
        },
        {
            "type": "text",
            "bbox": [
                0.091,
                0.798,
                0.392,
                0.813
            ],
            "angle": 0,
            "content": "令 \\(\\Sigma_0: z = 0 (x^2 + y^2 \\leqslant 4)\\)，取下侧，"
        },
        {
            "type": "equation",
            "bbox": [
                0.318,
                0.82,
                0.715,
                0.855
            ],
            "angle": 0,
            "content": "\\[\nI = \\iint_ {\\Sigma + \\Sigma_ {0}} y z \\mathrm {d} z \\mathrm {d} x + 2 \\mathrm {d} x \\mathrm {d} y - \\iint_ {\\Sigma_ {0}} y z \\mathrm {d} z \\mathrm {d} x + 2 \\mathrm {d} x \\mathrm {d} y,\n\\]"
        },
        {
            "type": "text",
            "bbox": [
                0.093,
                0.863,
                0.613,
                0.898
            ],
            "angle": 0,
            "content": "而 \\(\\iint_{\\Sigma + \\Sigma_0} yz \\, \\mathrm{d}z \\, \\mathrm{d}x + 2 \\, \\mathrm{d}x \\, \\mathrm{d}y = \\iiint_{\\Omega} z \\, \\mathrm{d}v = \\int_0^{2\\pi} \\, \\mathrm{d}\\theta \\int_0^{\\frac{\\pi}{2}} \\, \\mathrm{d}\\varphi \\int_0^2 r^3 \\sin \\varphi \\cos \\varphi \\, \\mathrm{d}r\\)"
        },
        {
            "type": "equation",
            "bbox": [
                0.291,
                0.907,
                0.574,
                0.933
            ],
            "angle": 0,
            "content": "\\[\n= 2 \\pi \\int_ {0} ^ {\\frac {\\pi}{2}} \\sin \\varphi \\cos \\varphi d \\varphi \\int_ {0} ^ {2} r ^ {3} d r = 4 \\pi ;\n\\]"
        }
    ],
    [
        {
            "type": "equation",
            "bbox": [
                0.107,
                0.069,
                0.595,
                0.109
            ],
            "angle": 0,
            "content": "\\[\n\\iint_ {\\Sigma_ {0}} y z \\mathrm {d} z \\mathrm {d} x + 2 \\mathrm {d} x \\mathrm {d} y = \\iint_ {\\Sigma_ {0}} 2 \\mathrm {d} x \\mathrm {d} y = - 2 \\iint_ {x ^ {2} + y ^ {2} \\leqslant 4} \\mathrm {d} x \\mathrm {d} y = - 8 \\pi ,\n\\]"
